    <refbody>
        <section id="section_usq_hc2_b3b">
            <title>Default Role</title>
            <p>Role for every user on this system. This role must only contain scopes that you are
                sure everyone has access to. </p>
        </section>
        <section id="section_lvf_mc2_b3b">
            <title>Management and Logs</title>
            <p>User role for processing logs, interface, operation and management functions,
                activation clients and resource management. </p>
        </section>
        <section id="section_ytc_pc2_b3b">
            <title>System Setup Manager</title>
            <p>Users of this role only have access to manage users and roles and must only be used
                at first-time setup.</p>
            <p>The default User Role assignment follows:</p>
